{"tid":168842,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次追日劇-逃恥 讀後感","createTime":"2017-03-23T21:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T17:26:24.000Z","uid":8203,"like":15,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb34db3c8596c841de453c99667c0a9e1aa1a85","tid":168842,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T21:50:01.000Z","msg":"嗚哇十一集咁就睇完 真係好撚唔捨得<br />\n利個申先：真係第一次追日劇（本身已經無乜睇電影劇）平時追開動畫<br />\n<br />\n逃恥真係神劇一套 好慶幸可以睇到 雖然遲左D<br />\n十一集既進展無冷場 每一集都有緊張位 唔長唔短<br />\n好撚過D劇用十鳩幾集鋪排<br />\n演員都好到位好有魅力每個角色都好引人入勝<br />\n唔使問啦結衣宇宙第一 雖然睇到錦戶亮既新聞扯火到升天<br />\n同埋睇日劇真係獲益良多 尤其我呢種嚮往日本既人<br />\n係日劇體會到真正既日語（同動畫語氣差好遠）<br />\n又可以了解現今日本文化<br />\n<br />\n最重要係一套劇輕巧咁表現到作者既思想<br />\n用角色既心底話/日常對話表達出自己既看法<br />\n教會觀眾一種平時無乜察覺既價值觀<br />\n得罪講句睇左咁多年tvb無一套及得上 不過我無睇天與地<br />\n<br />\n仲有片尾曲又好聽結衣又笑得咁靚隻舞又咁得意<br />\n真係錦上添花幫呢套劇昇華多個層次<br />\n<br />\n最後想問下各位日劇專家有無咩經典推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好係呢種有笑有淚又唔悶既日劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋小弟會計劃去下逃恥劇中聖地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9b678d319d8f66e41fb9e2f85269abd812d321","tid":168842,"uid":8203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:07:32.000Z","msg":"利申感受最深應該係第四集後面平匡要加班而風見邀請美栗共渡晚餐<br />\n<br />\n作為毒撚真係鄧平匡好撚心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己ot緊條女同第二條仔開開心心開酒飲<br />\n段獨白講佢以為美栗同佢一樣都係不被需要既人<br />\n好似搵到天涯鄰落人<br />\n後來有風見先發覺唔係 始終自己先係孤獨既人<br />\n一句「被愛的人真好呢」可見佢咁多年人黎都好缺愛<br />\n真係大魔法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O98c5P6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO98c5P6.jpg&h=a646f22b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到我都眼濕濕"},{"pid":"23611e505570e7526497b905176e9a270fac6457","tid":168842,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:21:58.000Z","msg":"毒撚精神食糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8873dae2ef1e82343900e408a06fafb7efb6c4","tid":168842,"uid":13245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:24:10.000Z","msg":"係時候要做痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2febe2f5cd0351b2bf76389d0d873d3e44c7c77","tid":168842,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係時候要做痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI'm ready.<br />\n不過應該唔係套套都岩我胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf65a9e6ae5c74513a9f16efd79001ce424d8df","tid":168842,"uid":69335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:35:26.000Z","msg":"假如毒撚睇呢套不可能不代入喇，結衣咁sweet, 仲要主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08493413f55a8fe71c744e0e7493fee83ccc5d65","tid":168842,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假如毒撚睇呢套不可能不代入喇，結衣咁sweet, 仲要主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFf指數爆燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c0b89cf4173cac0a59ec50d1665b8bb5dbbc20","tid":168842,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:38:30.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n深夜食堂 後呢套第二套日劇<br />\n好睇到仆街 結衣bb又靚又可愛<br />\n最後一集果句 <br />\n希望我們都能從束縛我們的一切中解放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高層次過韓狗劇不知幾多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入坑變左結衣痴線佬"},{"pid":"4b247addbd8d358bef70f4cbb2b19f7e55fac865","tid":168842,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係時候要做痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI'm ready.<br />\n不過應該唔係套套都岩我胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你下一套就係今日子"},{"pid":"bff9bd4a1521d2513e4d6f3857018b8fc68855dd","tid":168842,"uid":69335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T23:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>假如毒撚睇呢套不可能不代入喇，結衣咁sweet, 仲要主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFf指數爆燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n破處嗰幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b969fd5eda692afbf44439dc638eb6c1b9a08a7e","tid":168842,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:49:54.000Z","msg":"結衣其他個啲都好好睇<br />\n初出道個陣龍櫻做mk妹<br />\n之後全開女孩做菁英律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他神級日劇：<br />\n交響情人夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇者義彥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仁醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhero<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推理偵探醫療個啲冇乜邊套好睇<br />\n套套差唔多"},{"pid":"523e19b28918fda416c520ef0a88f77a7b264d49","tid":168842,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假如毒撚睇呢套不可能不代入喇，結衣咁sweet, 仲要主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最尾被個仆街阿頭炒左<br />\n明明表現最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又為公司仆心仆命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係因為佢係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係結衣仲同佢一齊真係好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e060efa7a547adaddd8d6702b2964c32d0cdefab","tid":168842,"uid":8542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"今日子<br />\n飛翔公關室<br />\nLegal high <br />\nCode blue<br />\n父女七日變<br />\nMy boss my hero<br />\n等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cead7c73d931495fa60250d246181af92cf31b","tid":168842,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日子<br />\n飛翔公關室<br />\nLegal high <br />\nCode blue<br />\n父女七日變<br />\nMy boss my hero<br />\n等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飛翔爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ddd605deb2a38f5fc8499fe41c71fab312dd76","tid":168842,"uid":18748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:57:51.000Z","